    "long_instructions": "## Tell a Persuasive Data Story with AI\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to analyze the datasets and tell a persuasive data story.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nDo This:\r\n1. Upload the **PDF file** of the dataset you looked at from the library.\r\n2. Ask AI Chat these questions:\r\n   - *Here’s a dataset. Help me write a persuasive data story based on this data.*",
